Quiz 11 Genre and Video Game Types

1. What could be considered the opposit of a real-time strategy game?

- a turn-based puzzle game with no strategic component like Tic Tac Toe

2. Rank the following genres based time sensitive gameplay. Put the most time sensitive first.

- A : Action games
- C : Real-time strategy games
- D : Action Role-playing games
- B : Turn-based strategy games

3. Which category best fits the following characteristics?

Exploration
Skill Levels
Inventory

- Role-playing games

4. A first person shooter is part of which greater category?

- Action games

5. In which category is direct control of the character a defining characteristic?

- Action games